Season 1

Episode 1: Doing it

This episode starts off the show. not needing much of a plot, this episode will tell you what this is show is all about

Episode 2: No Gay Thursday

Jacob badly wants to "get all creamy", but according to Braydon it is "no gay thursday"

Episode 3: Shorts

this episode is short and is all about shorts. considered as the lowest EP in the season

Episode 4: Taco Bell

Both Jacob and Braydon fall victim to the Blood God that is Taco Bell

Episode 5: Origin Story

the orgigin story of the Jraydon relationship. forever canonizing the fact that Jacobs old haircut making him look like a girl is the reason they are together

Episode 6: Special Guest

Braydon does it with a Special Guest: Mathew, who will inevitably become Jacobs nemisis

Episode 7: Finale

Its the end of school and jacob and braydon will have to separate. beutifully signaling the end of the first season
